lead_paragraph: FIFA President Gianni Infantino dangled the carrot of more World Cup spots for Asia during a visit to Seoul on Wednesday but while the Swiss was keen to press his case for an enlarged 40-team tournament, he will not try to twist anyone's arm.

headline.print_headline: Infantino Brings Vision of New FIFA to Asia
headline.main: Infantino Brings Vision of New FIFA to Asia
